{"title":"在天安门前","authors":["陈毅"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":4,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天安门前  陈毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门前似海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽是紧张，尽是繁忙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车辆运送忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地下管道安装忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地上绿化忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几座大建筑的脚手架"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸入云压低宫墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几台大吊车在屋顶上吊运忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它忙于安装几十吨重的大钢梁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真紧张，真繁忙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要建造几座高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要开辟一个大广场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这高楼能容纳万人会议，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这广场能使几百万军民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"列队成行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强大的新中国的首都，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应该有这种雄伟的规模。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那狭窄的旧世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连这想也不敢想！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这太紧张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这太繁忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是血肉做的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样繁忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怕就是钢铁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也要磨光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈哈，同志！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活就是紧张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也免不了繁忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界有地方是饥饿的紧张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界有地方是失业的繁忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比如我中国先前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被侵略难道还轻松？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反内战难道一点儿不忙？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两者比较来一个选择："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我宁愿现在这样的紧张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在这样的繁忙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂！请看工地上的工人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的意志多么坚强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的工作多么有组织。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们经得起紧张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们不怕什么繁忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们为建设打冲锋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们为建设作榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们与全国人民一道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把新中国的建设扛在肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国的建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正发出万道光芒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上凌宇宙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下照四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢断言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国的诅咒者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与破坏者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定被我们战败，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向我们投降。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（原载“中国青年”）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}